<div id="j-card" class="xcy-card fn-pt30 fn-pb30 fn-pl40 fn-clear">   <ul>          <li>              <div class="picbar">                                    <div class="content j-edit" data-id="1505204295390237">今天，我们探秘人防工程的直播就要给大家说再见了，我们下次再见，感谢各位网友的支持！</div>       </div>              <div class="action fn-clear">         <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left fn-ellipsis creater"><i class="pz-icon icon-account"></i> 刘书香</span>                  <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left"><i class="pz-icon icon-clock"></i> 2017-09-12 16:18</span>         <a class="j-view" href="javascript:void(0)" data-id="1505204295390237">预览</a>                         </div>     </li>          <li>              <div class="picbar">                                    <div class="content j-edit" data-id="1505204278449235">解除警报：是空袭已经结束，空袭警报解除。音响信号：连续长鸣1长声，时间为3分钟。解除警报并不意味着危险不复存在，要有组织的撤出隐蔽地区或危险区域，进入安全地带，遵守战时生产和生活秩序，积极协助有关部门尽快恢复生产和生活秩序，使受灾的损失降到最低限度。</div>       </div>              <div class="action fn-clear">         <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left fn-ellipsis creater"><i class="pz-icon icon-account"></i> 吕忆曦</span>                  <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left"><i class="pz-icon icon-clock"></i> 2017-09-12 16:17</span>         <a class="j-view" href="javascript:void(0)" data-id="1505204278449235">预览</a>                         </div>     </li>          <li>              <div class="picbar">                                    <div class="content j-edit" data-id="1505204260741233">空袭警报：是敌空袭兵器已临近城市，空袭即将或已经开始，警告人们迅速按照要求采取隐蔽措施。音响信号规定：鸣6秒，停6秒，重复15次为一个周期，时间为3分钟。空袭警报鸣响时，携带好个人防护器材和应急包，迅速进入人防工程内或按事先选定的地方就地疏散或隐蔽。</div>       </div>              <div class="action fn-clear">         <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left fn-ellipsis creater"><i class="pz-icon icon-account"></i> 吕忆曦</span>                  <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left"><i class="pz-icon icon-clock"></i> 2017-09-12 16:17</span>         <a class="j-view" href="javascript:void(0)" data-id="1505204260741233">预览</a>                         </div>     </li>          <li>              <div class="picbar">                                    <div class="content j-edit" data-id="1505204232201231">预先警报：是预先告知人们敌人即将空袭城市，要求做好防空袭的各项准备工作。音响信号规定：鸣36秒，停24秒，重复三遍为一个周期，时间为3分钟。预先警报鸣响时，要准备个人防护器材，配齐个人防空应急包内的急需物品，明确人防工程位置及疏散转移路线。居室人员要关闭门窗，切断电源，熄灭炉火，关闭煤气、液化气等。</div>       </div>              <div class="action fn-clear">         <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left fn-ellipsis creater"><i class="pz-icon icon-account"></i> 吕忆曦</span>                  <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left"><i class="pz-icon icon-clock"></i> 2017-09-12 16:17</span>         <a class="j-view" href="javascript:void(0)" data-id="1505204232201231">预览</a>                         </div>     </li>          <li>              <div class="picbar">                                    <div class="content j-edit" data-id="1505204206418229">国家规定防空袭警报信号分为预先警报、空袭警报、解除警报三种。</div>       </div>              <div class="action fn-clear">         <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left fn-ellipsis creater"><i class="pz-icon icon-account"></i> 吕忆曦</span>                  <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left"><i class="pz-icon icon-clock"></i> 2017-09-12 16:16</span>         <a class="j-view" href="javascript:void(0)" data-id="1505204206418229">预览</a>                         </div>     </li>          <li>              <div class="picbar">                                             <span class="type">多图</span>                           <div class="title fn-ellipsis">内江市城区已建有很多人防工程，比如：大千园、福都广场、汉安国际、市国税局、内江日报社等等。
                    防空地下室的设计、施工必须达到国家规定的防护标准和质量标准，平时可以增强楼房稳定性，战时具有防空功能。而普通地下室没有防护要求，不具有战时防护功能。直观地讲，防空地下室的防护等级比普通地下室要高，并安装有密闭门、防护密闭门和密闭阀门等防护设备。</div>                  <div class="pic j-edit" data-id="1505204173460227"><img src="https://xcycdn.zhongguowangshi.com/portrait/0f801266-ec69-4008-9bfe-59ca35ed91db.jpg?x-oss-process=image/resize,w_376"></div>       </div>              <div class="action fn-clear">         <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left fn-ellipsis creater"><i class="pz-icon icon-account"></i> 刘书香</span>                  <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left"><i class="pz-icon icon-clock"></i> 2017-09-12 16:16</span>         <a class="j-view" href="javascript:void(0)" data-id="1505204173460227">预览</a>                         </div>     </li>          <li>              <div class="picbar">                                             <span class="type">多图</span>                           <div class="title fn-ellipsis">商场内的防空知识</div>                  <div class="pic j-edit" data-id="1505204162424701"><img src="https://xcycdn.zhongguowangshi.com/portrait/494e1410-949e-4a1e-aa78-032a0aba402c.jpg?x-oss-process=image/resize,w_376"></div>       </div>              <div class="action fn-clear">         <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left fn-ellipsis creater"><i class="pz-icon icon-account"></i> 吕忆曦</span>                  <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left"><i class="pz-icon icon-clock"></i> 2017-09-12 16:16</span>         <a class="j-view" href="javascript:void(0)" data-id="1505204162424701">预览</a>                         </div>     </li>          <li>              <div class="picbar">                                    <span class="type">视频</span>                  <div class="title fn-ellipsis">洞天商场内部情况</div>                  <div class="pic j-edit" data-id="1505203954990205"><img src="https://xcycdn-video.zhongguowangshi.com/report-video/235c3574-cc3f-43ef-80a0-f217dc721c71_1000.jpg?x-oss-process=image/resize,w_376"></div>       </div>              <div class="action fn-clear">         <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left fn-ellipsis creater"><i class="pz-icon icon-account"></i> 刘书香</span>                  <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left"><i class="pz-icon icon-clock"></i> 2017-09-12 16:12</span>         <a class="j-view" href="javascript:void(0)" data-id="1505203954990205">预览</a>                         </div>     </li>          <li>              <div class="picbar">                                                      <div class="title fn-ellipsis">洞天商场属于坑道工事，约1978年建成，建筑面积9186平方米。平时用作商场，战时用作人员掩蔽，掩蔽人数7739人。由市人防办直接管理。2014年，市人防办立足于加强平战结合和消防安全管理，对洞天商场人防工程进行改造升级，将其打造成了我市一处具有鲜明特色的家具市场和平战结合亮点工程。近年来，该工程每年为社会提供就业岗位300余个，创税收100余万元。</div>                  <div class="pic j-edit" data-id="1505203777735695"><img src="https://xcycdn.zhongguowangshi.com/portrait/4a1af487-4a8b-4657-bf5e-ea571a6f6461.jpg?x-oss-process=image/resize,w_376"></div>       </div>              <div class="action fn-clear">         <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left fn-ellipsis creater"><i class="pz-icon icon-account"></i> 刘书香</span>                  <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left"><i class="pz-icon icon-clock"></i> 2017-09-12 16:09</span>         <a class="j-view" href="javascript:void(0)" data-id="1505203777735695">预览</a>                         </div>     </li>          <li>              <div class="picbar">                                    <div class="content j-edit" data-id="1505203681526203">下一站我们将去洞天商场</div>       </div>              <div class="action fn-clear">         <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left fn-ellipsis creater"><i class="pz-icon icon-account"></i> 刘书香</span>                  <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left"><i class="pz-icon icon-clock"></i> 2017-09-12 16:08</span>         <a class="j-view" href="javascript:void(0)" data-id="1505203681526203">预览</a>                         </div>     </li>          <li>              <div class="picbar">                                             <span class="type">多图</span>                           <div class="title fn-ellipsis">地下商场人防工程的变电，排风设施。</div>                  <div class="pic j-edit" data-id="1505203476861225"><img src="https://xcycdn.zhongguowangshi.com/portrait/2b644105-7030-4426-955a-9ff26ab55dd9.jpg?x-oss-process=image/resize,w_376"></div>       </div>              <div class="action fn-clear">         <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left fn-ellipsis creater"><i class="pz-icon icon-account"></i> 吕忆曦</span>                  <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left"><i class="pz-icon icon-clock"></i> 2017-09-12 16:04</span>         <a class="j-view" href="javascript:void(0)" data-id="1505203476861225">预览</a>                         </div>     </li>          <li>              <div class="picbar">                                             <span class="type">多图</span>                           <div class="title fn-ellipsis">地下商场内部情况……</div>                  <div class="pic j-edit" data-id="1505203358170201"><img src="https://xcycdn.zhongguowangshi.com/portrait/5d5c7b0e-62bc-4f8a-9878-2a6818f35661.jpg?x-oss-process=image/resize,w_376"></div>       </div>              <div class="action fn-clear">         <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left fn-ellipsis creater"><i class="pz-icon icon-account"></i> 刘书香</span>                  <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left"><i class="pz-icon icon-clock"></i> 2017-09-12 16:02</span>         <a class="j-view" href="javascript:void(0)" data-id="1505203358170201">预览</a>                         </div>     </li>          <li>              <div class="picbar">                                                      <div class="title fn-ellipsis">地下商场人防工程入口</div>                  <div class="pic j-edit" data-id="1505203124620223"><img src="https://xcycdn.zhongguowangshi.com/portrait/447a49e2-870d-47fe-bf18-948377692a34.jpg?x-oss-process=image/resize,w_376"></div>       </div>              <div class="action fn-clear">         <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left fn-ellipsis creater"><i class="pz-icon icon-account"></i> 吕忆曦</span>                  <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left"><i class="pz-icon icon-clock"></i> 2017-09-12 15:58</span>         <a class="j-view" href="javascript:void(0)" data-id="1505203124620223">预览</a>                         </div>     </li>          <li>              <div class="picbar">                           <span class="j-commentNum top topnum" data-id="1505203007569691">1条评论</span>                                    <span class="type">多图</span>                           <div class="title fn-ellipsis">你知道我们平时接触的小区地下车库属于人防工程吗？小区地下车库，如果是按人防部门批准修建的防空地下室，则属于人防工程；否则只是一般的普通地下室。</div>                  <div class="pic j-edit" data-id="1505203007569691"><img src="https://xcycdn.zhongguowangshi.com/portrait/f085e476-5619-4e81-b5b9-ef3d42df1f04.jpg?x-oss-process=image/resize,w_376"></div>       </div>              <div class="action fn-clear">         <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left fn-ellipsis creater"><i class="pz-icon icon-account"></i> 刘书香</span>                  <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left"><i class="pz-icon icon-clock"></i> 2017-09-12 15:56</span>         <a class="j-view" href="javascript:void(0)" data-id="1505203007569691">预览</a>                         </div>     </li>          <li>              <div class="picbar">                                    <div class="content j-edit" data-id="1505202935275689">地下商场属于单建式工事，建成于90年代，建筑面积2076平方米。平时用作商场，战时用作人员掩蔽，掩蔽人数1865人。由市人防办直接管理。</div>       </div>              <div class="action fn-clear">         <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left fn-ellipsis creater"><i class="pz-icon icon-account"></i> 吕忆曦</span>                  <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left"><i class="pz-icon icon-clock"></i> 2017-09-12 15:55</span>         <a class="j-view" href="javascript:void(0)" data-id="1505202935275689">预览</a>                         </div>     </li>          <li>              <div class="picbar">                                    <span class="type">视频</span>                  <div class="title fn-ellipsis">向地下商场人防工程行进中</div>                  <div class="pic j-edit" data-id="1505202848464199"><img src="https://xcycdn-video.zhongguowangshi.com/report-video/80d42ea6-8e88-4f81-b759-6c2600ae1ea2_1000.jpg?x-oss-process=image/resize,w_376"></div>       </div>              <div class="action fn-clear">         <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left fn-ellipsis creater"><i class="pz-icon icon-account"></i> 吕忆曦</span>                  <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left"><i class="pz-icon icon-clock"></i> 2017-09-12 15:54</span>         <a class="j-view" href="javascript:void(0)" data-id="1505202848464199">预览</a>                         </div>     </li>          <li>              <div class="picbar">                                             <span class="type">多图</span>                           <div class="title fn-ellipsis">现在是和平时期，绝大多数群众对于人民防空工作不是很了解，那么什么是人民防空？是指国家根据国防需要，动员和组织人民群众防备敌人空中袭击、消除空袭后果所采取的行动，其目的是通过动员和组织群众采取防护措施，防范和减轻空袭危害，以保护人民的生命和财产安全。人民防空简称人防，在国外，多把民众参与实施的战时防空与平时救灾相结合，称为民防。我国人民防空实行长期准备、重点建设、平战结合的方针，贯彻与经济建设协调发展、与城市建设相结合的原则。近年来，随着人防建设与经济社会发展的深度融合，其民防职能也得到了积极拓展。目前，全国多数地方的人防办兼挂民防局牌子，同时承担着应急救灾等民防职能。</div>                  <div class="pic j-edit" data-id="1505202689755197"><img src="https://xcycdn.zhongguowangshi.com/portrait/82d41d38-7ca8-4549-aa4a-cbb5bddd6545.jpg?x-oss-process=image/resize,w_376"></div>       </div>              <div class="action fn-clear">         <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left fn-ellipsis creater"><i class="pz-icon icon-account"></i> 刘书香</span>                  <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left"><i class="pz-icon icon-clock"></i> 2017-09-12 15:51</span>         <a class="j-view" href="javascript:void(0)" data-id="1505202689755197">预览</a>                         </div>     </li>          <li>              <div class="picbar">                                    <span class="type">视频</span>                  <div class="title fn-ellipsis">该机动指挥平台建成以来，市人防办组织专业人员刻苦钻研，在较短时间内熟练掌握了操作技能。先后参加内江市防灾救灾综合实战演练、四川省5.12防灾救灾大演练、四川省军区“天府使命—2014”实兵演习，均圆满完成了通信保障任务。</div>                  <div class="pic j-edit" data-id="1505202589386221"><img src="https://xcycdn-video.zhongguowangshi.com/report-video/1d6a84f1-dc61-4256-8b3e-bef757e9b9d4_1000.jpg?x-oss-process=image/resize,w_376"></div>       </div>              <div class="action fn-clear">         <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left fn-ellipsis creater"><i class="pz-icon icon-account"></i> 吕忆曦</span>                  <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left"><i class="pz-icon icon-clock"></i> 2017-09-12 15:49</span>         <a class="j-view" href="javascript:void(0)" data-id="1505202589386221">预览</a>                         </div>     </li>          <li>              <div class="picbar">                                             <span class="type">多图</span>                           <div class="title fn-ellipsis">内江市是国家三类人防重点城市。内江市人防办始建于1953年，在2010年政府机构改革中，由议事协调机构调整为市政府工作部门，接受军地双重领导。</div>                  <div class="pic j-edit" data-id="1505202466327219"><img src="https://xcycdn.zhongguowangshi.com/portrait/d34c9714-c688-46b2-bda8-3aacf9dd435c.jpg?x-oss-process=image/resize,w_376"></div>       </div>              <div class="action fn-clear">         <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left fn-ellipsis creater"><i class="pz-icon icon-account"></i> 刘书香</span>                  <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left"><i class="pz-icon icon-clock"></i> 2017-09-12 15:47</span>         <a class="j-view" href="javascript:void(0)" data-id="1505202466327219">预览</a>                         </div>     </li>          <li>              <div class="picbar">                                             <span class="type">多图</span>                           <div class="title fn-ellipsis">防空洞内部情况……</div>                  <div class="pic j-edit" data-id="1505202308579193"><img src="https://xcycdn.zhongguowangshi.com/portrait/4828de28-4960-4639-b17f-46d6707c4585.jpg?x-oss-process=image/resize,w_376"></div>       </div>              <div class="action fn-clear">         <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left fn-ellipsis creater"><i class="pz-icon icon-account"></i> 刘书香</span>                  <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left"><i class="pz-icon icon-clock"></i> 2017-09-12 15:45</span>         <a class="j-view" href="javascript:void(0)" data-id="1505202308579193">预览</a>                         </div>     </li>          <li>              <div class="picbar">                           <span class="j-commentNum top topnum" data-id="1505202178740213">1条评论</span>                           <span class="type">视频</span>                  <div class="title fn-ellipsis">大佛寺防空洞属于坑道工事，是东兴区政府办公室管理的单位人防工程，平时用于种菇、存放香蕉等，战时用作人员掩蔽。</div>                  <div class="pic j-edit" data-id="1505202178740213"><img src="https://xcycdn-video.zhongguowangshi.com/report-video/5530df8f-2fdc-43c6-9e43-4067d5689288_1000.jpg?x-oss-process=image/resize,w_376"></div>       </div>              <div class="action fn-clear">         <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left fn-ellipsis creater"><i class="pz-icon icon-account"></i> 刘书香</span>                  <span class="pz-label label-normal fn-left"><i class="pz-icon icon-clock"></i> 2017-09-12 15:42</span>         <a class="j-view" href="javascript:void(0)" data-id="1505202178740213">预览</a>                         </div>     </li>          <li>              <div class="picbar">                           <span class="j-commentNum top topnum" data-id="1505202177873211">1条评论</span>                                    <span class="type">多图</span>                           <div class="title fn-ellipsis">大佛寺防空洞属于坑道工事，是东兴区政府办公室管理的单位人防工程，平时用于种菇、存放香蕉等，战时用作人员掩蔽。</div>                  <div class="pic j-edit" data-id="1505202177873211"><img src="https://xcycdn.zhongguowangshi.com/portrait/9cdde49b-848b-4c36-aaf4-39396b17ce38.jpg?x-oss-process=image/resize,w_3